    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mandatory custodial sentence and compensation for child neglect",
        "additional_details": "Too many children in the UK are neglected daily and although they are removed from the situation, sometimes it seems like the parent/guardian gets away with the situation. Child neglect should be a offence where a custodial sentence is received and the child receive compensation for their suffering",
        "background": "Anyone who commits an offence of child neglect to receive a custodial sentence and be made to pay compensation to the child they have neglected",
